/**** LIBRARIES *****/

- Retrofit
In this project I used the Retrofit library to integrate with the google maps API.
I could have used AsyncTasks to perform this, but the use of this library makes development faster and has better performance.
In the link below you can check a comparison between Retrofit, Volley and AsyncTasks and understand why my choice.

http://themakeinfo.com/2015/04/retrofit-android-tutorial/